    <div class="content"><p>The basic idea in the comic books was that the Cylons had the humans on the ropes and pulled out the first time with a strict understanding that the humans kept their nose out of the Cylons business. The humans crossed the armistice line and the Cylons viewed that as a sign of the human's true nature. Total Annihilation wasn't a question of if after that point but when.</p>
