    <div class="content"><p>Leaving aside the "god" element - the whole cyclical element of "all this has happened before" would have been SO much more resonant if there had been one more cycle - ie the final Earth was ours but had finally healed over time, the radioactive Earth was where "we" went next, and the now radioactive Caprica (etc) was the most recent repeat of destruction.  </p>
