    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/battlestars-daybreak-worst-ending-history-screen-science-fiction#comment-10074" class="active">This series is not over......</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by FOR_CE (not verified) on Wed, 2009-07-15 22:36.</div>
