<p>On the nano-Cylon thing: I understand the upcoming Doctor Who deals with entities propogated via communications, and the ongoing comic Existence 2.0 deals with conciousness transmission after physical death. I'm not sure how it would work but I'd take a meta-conciousness approach to the head characters: they're an emergent property - a natural, inevitable, and necessary glitch in the system.</p>
